msgid "0:ノアⅡ。災厄をもたらすもの。あるいは人類の理想郷を作るもの。[%p]"
msgstr "0:Noah II, bringer of disaster, or perhaps the creator of mankind's utopia.[%p]"

msgid "100:どちらだろうと、梨深にとってはあまり意味がなかった。[linebreak]どちらだろうと、梨深にとってそれは“壊すべきもの”だったから。[%p]"
msgstr "100:Rimi didn't really care which. Whichever it was, she was going to destroy it.[%p]"

msgid "200:ノアⅡの場所は、梨深には分かっていた。[linebreak]静かに、そして巧妙に人々の意識の中に埋め込まれた、周囲共通認識。[%p]"
msgstr "200:Rimi knew where Noah II was. A shared awareness, quietly and cleverly slipped into the human mind.[%p]"

msgid "300:渋谷の駅の目の前にありながら。[linebreak]数年前に取り壊された建物でありながら。[%p]"
msgstr "300:It was right in front of Shibuya Station. It was in a building that had supposedly been torn down years ago.[%p]"

msgid "400:誰も疑問に思わずそこにあり。[linebreak]誰も足を踏み入れてこようとはしない。[%p]"
msgstr "400:Nobody suspected a thing. Nobody went inside.[%p]"

msgid "500:人の気配がしない、かつてプラネタリウムだったその扉を開いて、梨深は中へと踏み込んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "500:Rimi opened the door to what had once been a planetarium, and stepped inside.[%p]"

msgid "600:そこに広がる光景に、梨深は目を見開いた。[linebreak]あまりにも巨大な、怪物を思わせる『装置』。[linebreak]それが、ドーム状の部屋の中央に鎮座していた。[%p]"
msgstr "600:Her eyes went wide when she saw what was inside. It was a device, impossibly huge and monstrous. The room was dome-like, with the device at its center.[%p]"

msgid "700:広い室内には、不気味な音がかすかに響いている。[linebreak]それは低く、獣がうなるような音。[linebreak]『装置』が稼働していることを意味する音。[%p]"
msgstr "700:There was a small, eerie sound that echoed throughout the huge space. It was low, like a beast's growling. The sound meant the device was online.[%p]"

msgid "800:ノアⅡ――[%p]"
msgstr "800:Noah II...[%p]"

msgid "900:[name]梨深[line]「ナナちゃん……！」[%p]"
msgstr "900:[name]梨深[line]Nana![%p]"

msgid "1000:西條七海が、その装置のすぐ横に囚われていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:Nanami Nishijo was being held right next to it.[%p]"

msgid "1100:破れかけた制服、血がにじんだ右手の包帯、力なく垂れた頭。ひどく青ざめた顔色。[linebreak]その痛々しい姿に、梨深は言葉を失う。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:Her uniform was torn. There was a bloody bandage on her right hand, and her head was slumped forward, limp. She was terribly pale, too. Rimi was struck wordless at the sight.[%p]"

msgid "1200:磔にされたナザレのイエスのごとく。[linebreak]いや、七海を捕らえているのは、十字架と呼べる代物ではない。[linebreak]それとはかけ離れた、あまりにも悪意に満ちた形状。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:Like Jesus, nailed to a cross. No, it wasn't a cross that held her captive. It was a terrible, almost malicious shape.[%p]"

msgid "1300:この世のすべての邪悪――[linebreak]この世のすべての混沌――[linebreak]この世のすべての背徳――[%p]"
msgstr "1300:All the evil in the world... All the chaos in the world... All the wickedness in the world...[%p]"

msgid "1400:それらを形として表象させたものと言っても過言ではなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:It was all of these things, and more.[%p]"

msgid "1500:梨深は警戒しながら、素早く周囲を見回す。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:Rimi quickly and cautiously looked around.[%p]"

msgid "1600:七海以外に人影はない。[linebreak]ノアⅡの開発を主導し、かつて梨深に残酷な拷問を行ったあの男――野呂瀬玄一の姿は見当たらなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:There was no one else in the room but Nanami. She was looking for Genichi Norose, the man who was once her torturer and was now the leader of the Noah II project. But he wasn't here.[%p]"

msgid "1700:梨深は意外に思いつつも、七海を助けることを優先し、彼女を磔にしているオブジェへと駆け寄った。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:She was surprised, but she decided to prioritize saving Nanami. She ran over to the strange object holding her.[%p]"

msgid "1800:[name]梨深[line]「ナナちゃん、しっかり」[%p]"
msgstr "1800:[name]梨深[line]Nana! Wake up![%p]"

msgid "1900:[name]七海[line]「う……うう……」[%p]"
msgstr "1900:[name]七海[line]Aah... Aah...[%p]"

msgid "2000:オブジェから七海を下ろし、七海に息があることを確認してホッとする。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:She brought Nanami down, and was relieved to see she was still breathing.[%p]"

msgid "2100:ひとまず七海をどこか安全な場所に連れていかなくちゃ。[linebreak]梨深は七海を抱き上げようとした。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:The first thing she had to do was get her somewhere safe. She went to help her up.[%p]"

msgid "2200:だが――[%p]"
msgstr "2200:But...[%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]梨深[line]「がはっ……！？」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]梨深[line]Gwah![%p]"

msgid "2400:背中に激痛。[linebreak]抉られるような。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:A terrible pain in her back. Like something tearing through her.[%p]"

msgid "2500:梨深は血を吐いた。[linebreak]その血が、七海の服にかかる。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:Rimi spat up blood. The blood fell on Nanami's clothes.[%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「久々の再会だというのに、私には挨拶もなしですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]野呂瀬[line]It's been so long since we've met, and you're not even going to say hello?[%p]"

msgid "2700:痛みをこらえ、振り返る。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:She turned around, trying to hold back to the pain.[%p]"

msgid "2800:野呂瀬玄一が、すぐ背後に立っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:Genichi Norose was standing right there.[%p]"

msgid "2900:その手には――[%p]"
msgstr "2900:In his hand...[%p]"

msgid "3000:直前まで七海を捕らえていたオブジェ。[linebreak]それはオブジェではなく、剣。[linebreak]野呂瀬玄一の、ディソード。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:was the strange object that had been holding Nanami. It was a sword. It was Genichi Norose's Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "3100:そのディソードが、梨深の身体に突き刺さっている。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:And now, it was stabbing into her body.[%p]"

msgid "3200:野呂瀬が手をゆっくりと引く。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:Norose slowly pulled back his hand.[%p]"

msgid "3300:身体に食い込んでいた、ディソードの鋭い刃が、梨深の肉の上を滑り、骨の表面を擦る。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:The sharp blades of the Di-Sword slid through her body, cutting into her bones.[%p]"

msgid "3400:身を削られるような激痛に、梨深は弓なりに身体を痙攣させた。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:Rimi arched her back and began to flail from the pain.[%p]"

msgid "3500:[name]梨深[line]「う、ああぁっ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "3500:[name]梨深[line]Uwaaaah![%p]"

msgid "3600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「痛みには慣れているはずでしょう？」[%p]"
msgstr "3600:[name]野呂瀬[line]I thought you'd be used to pain by now.[%p]"

msgid "3700:野呂瀬の剣が、梨深の身体から抜けた。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:Norose's blade left her body.[%p]"

msgid "3800:大量の血が溢れ出す。[linebreak]身体じゅうの神経が悲鳴を上げる。[linebreak]痛みで今にも気絶しそうだった。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:Her blood poured out everywhere. All the nerves inside her were screaming. The pain threatened to make her pass out.[%p]"

msgid "3900:[name]野呂瀬[line]「その娘は、西條拓巳をおびき寄せる貴重な餌なのです。勝手に連れて行かれては困りますね」[%p]"
msgstr "3900:[name]野呂瀬[line]That girl is my bait. She's how I'm going to lure Takumi Nishijo here. I can't have you taking her.[%p]"

msgid "4000:[name]梨深[line]「……うぅ」[%p]"
msgstr "4000:[name]梨深[line]Ah...?![%p]"

msgid "4100:野呂瀬のギガロマニアックスとしての力の強大さを、梨深はよく知っている。[linebreak]なにしろ、この男に３年以上もの間、捕らわれていたのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:Rimi knew exactly how powerful a Gigalomaniac Norose was. He'd held her for over three years.[%p]"

msgid "4200:まともにやりあっても勝ち目はない。[linebreak]かと言ってこのまま逃がしてもらえるわけもない。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:She couldn't beat him in a head-on fight. But she knew he wouldn't let her escape, either.[%p]"

msgid "4300:――せめて、ナナちゃんだけでも逃がさなきゃ。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:—At least, I have to get Nana out of here.[%p]"

msgid "4400:口の中に、血の味が広がっている。[linebreak]激しい嘔吐感がさっきから断続的にこみ上げてきている。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:The taste of blood was filling her mouth. She kept feeling a violent urge to vomit.[%p]"

msgid "4500:背中の傷口は火で炙られ続けているかのように熱く。[linebreak]痛みのせいで身体は満足に動かせず。[linebreak]血は際限なくにじみ出している。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:The open wound on her back burned like it was on fire. She could barely move from the pain, and the blood just kept coming.[%p]"

msgid "4600:意識が途切れそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:She almost passed out.[%p]"

msgid "4700:とても寒い。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:It was so cold.[%p]"

msgid "4800:目がかすむ。[linebreak]その視界の中で、野呂瀬が嘲るような笑みを浮かべている。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:Her vision was going blurry. She could just barely make out the cruel smile on Norose's face.[%p]"

msgid "4900:ダメかもしれない――[%p]"
msgstr "4900:Maybe this was the end.[%p]"

msgid "5000:梨深には自分がこの男から逃れる未来を妄想することができない。[linebreak]心を占めるのはただ絶望だけ。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:Rimi couldn't even imagine a situation where she'd escape alive. The only thoughts in her mind were of pure despair.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]タクミ[line]「僕の力を、あげるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]タクミ[line]I'll give you my power.[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]梨深[line]「……！？」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]梨深[line]...?![%p]"

msgid "5300:その声は、梨深にとって聞き覚えのあるものだった。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:It was a voice she recognized.[%p]"

msgid "5400:ニシジョウタクミ。[linebreak]あるいは『将軍』と名乗る少年。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:Takumi Nishijo... The boy who called himself Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "5500:声は遠隔からの、いわばテレパシーのようなものだ。[linebreak]思考盗撮と同じ原理。[linebreak]ギガロマニアックスだからこそできる芸当。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:The voice was coming from far away, like telepathy. It used the same principles as mind reading, a power that only Gigalomaniacs had.[%p]"

msgid "5600:[name]タクミ[line]「僕の最期の妄想を、君に」[%p]"
msgstr "5600:[name]タクミ[line]I'll give you my final delusion.[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]梨深[line]「タクミ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]梨深[line]Takumi?[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]タクミ[line]「君に、こんな辛い役目を任せてしまって、ごめん」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]タクミ[line]I'm sorry that you have to be the one to do something so hard.[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]タクミ[line]「もう、余計なことは言わない。君の意志を曲げることは無理だって、分かったから」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]タクミ[line]I won't try to change your mind anymore. I know it's impossible now.[%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]タクミ[line]「死ぬつもり、なんだね？」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]タクミ[line]You plan on dying here, don't you?[%p]"

msgid "6100:――死なずになんとかできる方法があったなら、そうしてたけど。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:—If there was a way to get out of this alive, I would've taken it.[%p]"

msgid "6200:[name]タクミ[line]「“彼”が目覚めなかった以上、僕にはどうすることもできない」[%p]"
msgstr "6200:[name]タクミ[line]He didn't wake up. Now, there's nothing I can do.[%p]"

msgid "6300:[name]タクミ[line]「だからせめて、僕の最期の妄想を、君に」[%p]"
msgstr "6300:[name]タクミ[line]But at least... I can give you my final delusion.[%p]"

msgid "6400:[name]梨深[line]「な、なに言ってるの！？\u3000あなたはそんなことしなくても――」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]梨深[line]W-What are you talking about? You don't need to—[%p]"

msgid "6500:梨深は、この場にいない相手に向かって叫んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:Rimi screamed out to a person who wasn't even here.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]タクミ[line]「君だけを、死なせるわけにはいかないよ。すべての元凶は僕なんだから」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]タクミ[line]I can't let you be the one to die here when I'm the one who caused all this.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]梨深[line]「だって……！」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]梨深[line]But...[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]タクミ[line]「もういいんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]タクミ[line]Enough.[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]タクミ[line]「梨深、野呂瀬を……殺してほしい。ノアⅡを、破壊してほしい」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]タクミ[line]Rimi... I want you to kill Norose. I want you to destroy Noah II.[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]タクミ[line]「僕が、サポートするから」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]タクミ[line]I'll help you.[%p]"

msgid "7100:梨深は唇を噛み、涙を拭い、遠のきそうになる意識を必死にたぐり寄せた。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:Rimi bit her lip, wiped away her tears, and tried her best to keep herself from passing out.[%p]"

msgid "7200:ディソードをリアルブート。[linebreak]ひらひらと、無数の輝く羽根が舞い散る。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:She real booted her Di-Sword. Countless feathers fell from the sky.[%p]"

msgid "7300:七海を片手に抱いたまま、梨深は剣を構えた。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:She raised the sword, holding Nanami in one hand.[%p]"

msgid "7400:ボタボタと、大量の血痕が足許に垂れる。[linebreak]血は、いまだ止まらない。[linebreak]止まるような傷ではない。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:Blood was pooling at her feet. It hadn't stopped. It wasn't going to.[%p]"

msgid "7500:[name]野呂瀬[line]「ふんっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "7500:[name]野呂瀬[line]Hahh![%p]"

msgid "7600:野呂瀬のディソードによる、すべてをなぎ倒すかのような一閃。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:Norose brought his Di-Sword down on her.[%p]"

msgid "7700:梨深は七海をかばいつつ、剣で受け止める。[linebreak]しかし体重差は致命的であり。[linebreak]梨深の細い身体では野呂瀬の一撃を受け止めきれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:Rimi blocked with her own, making sure to keep Nanami away from the blade. But he was so much bigger than her. Her frail body couldn't handle the force of his attack.[%p]"

msgid "7800:吹っ飛ばされ、壁に激突。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:She flew backwards and collided with a wall.[%p]"

msgid "7900:[name]梨深[line]「く……」[%p]"
msgstr "7900:[name]梨深[line]...![%p]"

msgid "8000:プラネタリウムの、ドーム上の壁に亀裂が入る。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:A crack formed in the wall of the planetarium.[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]野呂瀬[line]「わざわざ生かしておいてやったというのに、恩を仇で返すとは」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]野呂瀬[line]I was kind enough to let you live, and this is how you repay my kindness?[%p]"

msgid "8200:[name]野呂瀬[line]「また、いたぶられたいのですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "8200:[name]野呂瀬[line]Did you not suffer enough pain the first time?[%p]"

msgid "8300:野呂瀬が、ゆっくりと梨深の方へと歩み寄ってくる。[linebreak]その顔に浮かぶのは、余裕。[linebreak]梨深を完全に見下している。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:Norose slowly began to walk toward her. There was confidence in his eyes. Rimi was no threat to him.[%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]梨深[line]「ヘ、ヘンタイだよね……あなたって」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]梨深[line]Y-You're a pervert, aren't you?[%p]"

msgid "8500:ニヤリと、梨深は笑う。けれどその笑みは引きつっている。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:Rimi grinned. But her grin was stiff and frozen on her face.[%p]"

msgid "8600:そしてなにを思ったか、背後のひび割れた壁に向けて剣を振るった。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:And then, for some reason, she swung her sword at the cracked wall behind her.[%p]"

msgid "8700:壁が崩れ、外の景色が露わになる。[linebreak]雨が降っていた。[linebreak]空には厚い雨雲が垂れ込めている。[%p]"
msgstr "8700:The wall fell away, revealing the sky outside. It was raining. Dark clouds were hanging low above them.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]野呂瀬[line]「逃げようとでも？」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]野呂瀬[line]Trying to run away?[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]梨深[line]「逃げないよ……でも……」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]梨深[line]I won't run away, but...[%p]"

msgid "9000:梨深は、抱いていた七海をその場に座らせた。[linebreak]剣を持ったまま、七海を背中から抱く。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:Rimi sat Nanami down on the ground. She held her from behind, keeping the Di-Sword in one hand.[%p]"

msgid "9100:[name]梨深[line]「ナナちゃんは……関係ないでしょ」[%p]"
msgstr "9100:[name]梨深[line]Nanami... has nothing to do with this.[%p]"

msgid "9200:梨深は妄想する。[linebreak]まばゆい閃光。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:Rimi created a delusion, a bright blast of light.[%p]"

msgid "9300:その光が収まったとき、梨深が持っていた翼のようなディソードは消え。[linebreak]代わりに、七海の背に純白の羽が生えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "9300:When it disappeared, her Di-Sword was gone, and instead, there were wings of the purest white on Nanami's back.[%p]"

msgid "9400:血に染まる七海の身体を、清浄なる翼が包む。[linebreak]その姿は、凄惨で、なおかつ美しい、さながら天使のよう。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:The white wings, impossibly pure, enveloped her bloody body. She was like an angel, her appearance horrible to look at, but still beautiful.[%p]"

msgid "9500:七海の意識はない。だがその羽は、自ら意志を持つかのように大きく羽ばたいた。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:Nanami was unconscious, but the wings took flight, as if they had a will of their own.[%p]"

msgid "9600:梨深が七海から離れる。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Rimi moved away from Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "9700:戸惑う野呂瀬の前で、プラネタリウムに開いた大きな穴をくぐり、七海は空へと飛び立つ。[%p]"
msgstr "9700:As Norose watched, confused, Nanami flew through the hole in the planetarium wall, and out into the sky around them.[%p]"

msgid "9800:ゆっくりと、雨が降りしきる渋谷の空を滑空していった。[%p]"
msgstr "9800:She glided slowly away in the rainy Shibuya sky.[%p]"

msgid "9900:梨深は丸腰で、それを見送る。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:Rimi watched her go, unarmed.[%p]"

msgid "10000:[name]梨深[line]「ナナちゃん、無事で……いて……」[%p]"
msgstr "10000:[name]梨深[line]Nana, please... be safe.[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]野呂瀬[line]「ディソードを妄想によって翼としたのですか」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]野呂瀬[line]So, you used your delusion to turn your Di-Sword into wings?[%p]"

msgid "10200:[name]野呂瀬[line]「……それで、君は逃げないのですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "10200:[name]野呂瀬[line]But you yourself aren't going to run?[%p]"

msgid "10300:すでに野呂瀬は、自らのディソードの間合いの内に梨深を捉えていた。[linebreak]腕を一振りするだけで、梨深の首は飛ぶ。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:Norose was close enough now to kill her with the sword. A single movement of his arm would sever her head.[%p]"

msgid "10400:梨深はしかし、物怖じしていない鋭い瞳で、野呂瀬を見据えた。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:She was watching him, however, with no fear in her eyes.[%p]"

msgid "10500:[name]梨深[line]「まだ、逃げられないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "10500:[name]梨深[line]I can't run yet.[%p]"

msgid "10600:[name]梨深[line]「……あなたを、殺さなきゃいけないから」[%p]"
msgstr "10600:[name]梨深[line]I have to kill you first.[%p]"

msgid "10700:懐から、黒光りする十字架を取り出す。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:She brought a gleaming cross out from her pocket.[%p]"

msgid "10800:正確にはそれは十字架ではなく、杭。[linebreak]『張り付け』事件で使われたものと同じもの。[linebreak]たった今、梨深がリアルブートした。[%p]"
msgstr "10800:It wasn't a cross. It was a stake. The same as the cross-shaped stakes used in the Crucified murder. Rimi had just real booted it.[%p]"

msgid "10900:野呂瀬はそれを見てせせら笑う。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:Norose chuckled as he looked at it.[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]野呂瀬[line]「私を殺す？\u3000そのような玩具でですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]野呂瀬[line]Kill me? With that toy?[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]野呂瀬[line]「ずいぶんと、ナメられたものですね」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]野呂瀬[line]You have no idea what I can do to you, do you?[%p]"

msgid "11200:その一撃は素早かった。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:His attack was fast.[%p]"

msgid "11300:野呂瀬の身の丈よりも巨大なディソードが、通常の物理法則では考えられない速度で、梨深の脇腹を切り裂いた。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:The Di-Sword he held was bigger than he was, and it slashed open her side with a speed that was impossible according to the laws of physics.[%p]"

msgid "11400:自分の身体が斬撃を受けよろめいたところで、梨深は自分が斬られたことに気付いた。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:Only after her body staggered from the impact did she realize she'd been cut.[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]梨深[line]「ああ、あああああ――！」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]梨深[line]Aaaaaaah![%p]"

msgid "11600:その場にくずおれて、梨深は痛みのあまり悲鳴を上げる。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:She collapsed, screaming from the pain.[%p]"

msgid "11700:野呂瀬の攻撃は殺すためのものではなかった。[linebreak]殺そうと思えばいつでもできたが、彼はあえてそうしなかった。[linebreak]のたうつ梨深に歩み寄り、腕を踏み付ける。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:Norose had deliberately used a less-than-lethal stroke. He could've killed her, but he chose not to. As she writhed on the ground in pain, he walked over to her and brought his foot down hard on her arm.[%p]"

msgid "11800:梨深は苦しげな呼吸を繰り返しつつも歯を食いしばり、動きを止めた。[linebreak]止めざるを得なかった。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:Gritting her teeth and panting for breath, she stopped moving. She had no choice but to stop moving.[%p]"

msgid "11900:野呂瀬の巨大な剣の切っ先が、梨深の血まみれになっている背中に突き立てられていた。けれどまだ、その切っ先が身を貫くことはない。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:The tip of Norose's massive Di-Sword was stabbed into her back. But he hadn't run her through yet.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]野呂瀬[line]「もう一度、聞かせてもらっていいでしょうか？」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]野呂瀬[line]Let me hear you say it again.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]梨深[line]「や、やめて……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]梨深[line]S-Stop...[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]野呂瀬[line]「やめませんよ」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]野呂瀬[line]No.[%p]"

msgid "12300:梨深の懇願に合わせて、野呂瀬はディソードを持つ手に力を込めた。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:He pressed down hard as she begged for him to stop.[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]梨深[line]「が、は、あ、ああああ――！」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]梨深[line]Gaah... Aahhh...[%p]"

msgid "12500:剣の先端がすでに血まみれになっている梨深の身をさらに抉り、深く食い込んでいく。それはまるで昆虫に虫ピンを刺しているかのようだった。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:The tip of the blade dug even deeper into her bloody body. It was like he was pinning an insect to a block.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「それで、私を殺すと言いましたか？\u3000それとも私の聞き間違いでしょうか？」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]野呂瀬[line]So, you said you were going to kill me? Or did I hear you wrong?[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]梨深[line]「はあっ、はあっ、ぐすっ、はあ、うぅ、く……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]梨深[line]Hahh... Hahh... Gwahh... Hahh... Ugh...[%p]"

msgid "12800:それでも梨深は、うつ伏せに倒れたまま片手を伸ばし、野呂瀬の足にすがりつく。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:Rimi was lying face down on the ground. She reached forward with one arm and grabbed Norose's leg.[%p]"

msgid "12900:涙で濡れた瞳の奥に、いまだ確固たる決意の炎を宿し。[linebreak]嘲笑する野呂瀬を、下からにらみつけて。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:There was a firm resolve burning deep within her tear-stained eyes. She glared up at Norose from below.[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]梨深[line]「……殺してあげる。あたしが、あなたを」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]梨深[line]Yeah... I'll kill you.[%p]"

msgid "13100:野呂瀬は剣を抜くと、梨深の顎を全力で蹴り上げた。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:Norose pulled out his sword and kicked her in the jaw as hard as he could,[%p]"

msgid "13200:彼女の身体が人形のように床の上を転がる。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:Her body rolled along the floor like a doll.[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]野呂瀬[line]「しばらく会わないうちに、実に不愉快な人間になったようですね」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]野呂瀬[line]You've grown to be quite the nasty little girl since we last met.[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]野呂瀬[line]「すでに君は用済みです。利用価値があるかと思い、生かしておきましたが……もういりません」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]野呂瀬[line]You're of no more value to me. I let you live because I thought you might be of some further use... but I have no further need of you.[%p]"

msgid "13500:すでに梨深は瀕死。[linebreak]なおも身体を起こし、野呂瀬の方へ這ってこようとしているが、ディソードもなくまともに歩くこともできないのでは、死んだも同然。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:Rimi was already at death's door. She'd gotten up and was trying to crawl towards me, but with no Di-Sword and no ability to walk, she was as good as dead.[%p]"

msgid "13600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「私に生意気な口を叩いたことを、後悔しながら死んでいってください。……例えば、そうですね、これから３０年ほど、私が君に毎日拷問を施してあげましょうか。……妄想の中でね」[%p]"
msgstr "13600:[name]野呂瀬[line]You're going to regret talking to me that way before you die. Hmm... perhaps I can spend the next thirty years torturing you every day. Inside a delusion, of course.[%p]"

msgid "13700:野呂瀬は唇を歪めた。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:Norose's lips twisted.[%p]"

msgid "13800:舞い散る羽根の中にうずくまる梨深を視界に捉え。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:He stared at Rimi as the feathers fell around him.[%p]"

msgid "13900:妄想する。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:He formed a delusion.[%p]"

msgid "14000:ディソードを強く握りしめ。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:He held his Di-Sword tight.[%p]"

msgid "14100:ディラックの海とのチャネルを広げる。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:He expanded the channel to the Dirac Sea.[%p]"

msgid "14200:彼の妄想を具現化するための、粒子と反粒子が生まれ。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:The particles and anti-particles needed to manifest his delusion were born.[%p]"

msgid "14300:そのうちの、粒子のみを。[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Of those, he took only the former,[%p]"

msgid "14400:光の信号であるところの“視線”によって――[%p]"
msgstr "14400:and sent them into Rimi Sakihata's dead spots,[%p]"

msgid "14500:咲畑梨深のデッドスポットへと送り込む――[%p]"
msgstr "14500:using his gaze.[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]梨深[line]「それを、待ってた――」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]梨深[line]That's what I've been waiting for.[%p]"

msgid "14700:[name]野呂瀬[line]「……なに？」[%p]"
msgstr "14700:[name]野呂瀬[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "14800:舞い散る羽根は、一瞬で“瞳”に変わる。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:In an instant, the feathers turned to eyes.[%p]"

msgid "14900:それまで、野呂瀬を見つめる瞳は、梨深のものだけだった。[linebreak]だがいまや野呂瀬を囲むのは、数え切れないほどの、空中に浮かぶ瞳。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Until that moment, the only eyes looking at Norose had been Rimi's. But now, he was surrounded by a thousand eyes, all floating in the air.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]梨深[line]「その目、だれの目？」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]梨深[line]Whose eyes are those?[%p]"

msgid "15100:それが、タクミから託された、最期の妄想。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:This was the final delusion that Takumi had given her.[%p]"

msgid "15200:野呂瀬が飛ばした粒子は、無数の瞳に阻まれ、梨深のデッドスポットには届かず。そしてそれらの瞳は、ディラックの海と繋がって反粒子を垂れ流す。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:The particles he'd created were blocked by innumerable eyes, and never reached her dead spots. And then all the eyes linked with the Dirac Sea, creating anti-particles of their own.[%p]"

msgid "15300:ギガロマニアックスの力を封じる、絶対防御。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:An impregnable defense against a Gigalomaniac's power...[%p]"

msgid "15400:ニシジョウタクミだからこそ。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Only Takumi Nishijo could create such a thing.[%p]"

msgid "15500:人間を１人、創造できるほどの力を持つギガロマニアックスだからこそ。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:Only a Gigalomaniac with enough power to give life to an entire human being was capable of such a feat.[%p]"

msgid "15600:己の命の最期の灯火を燃やし尽くしたからこそ。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:And even then, only by using the last dying embers of his life.[%p]"

msgid "15700:リアルブートすることのできた、化け物じみた妄想。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:A monstrous delusion, given life by real booting...[%p]"

msgid "15800:野呂瀬は瞳に囲まれ、愕然と息を呑む。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Norose gasped in shock as the eyes surrounded him.[%p]"

msgid "15900:どこを見渡しても、あるのは、彼を見つめてくる瞳ばかり。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:Wherever he looked, there were eyes, staring back at him.[%p]"

msgid "16000:その数は減るどころか、むしろ際限なく広がる。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:And more and more were appearing out of nowhere.[%p]"

msgid "16100:野呂瀬の視界すべてを、埋め尽くす。[linebreak]そして迫ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Soon he saw nothing but eyes. And the eyes were getting closer.[%p]"

msgid "16200:野呂瀬は本能的な恐怖に襲われた。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:An instinctive fear took over.[%p]"

msgid "16300:歯を食いしばり、ディソードを振り回す。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:He clenched his jaw and began to wildly flail about his Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "16400:斬られた瞳は血をまき散らしながら、まぶたを閉じ、消えてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:Blood spurted from the eyes he struck, and they closed and disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "16500:だがその瞳のさらに後ろに、別の瞳がいる。[linebreak]斬っても斬っても、瞳の数は減らず。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:But behind them were more. No matter how many he destroyed, more came.[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「わ、私を、見るな――」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]野呂瀬[line]D-Don't look at me![%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]梨深[line]「それなら、もう一生、目を開けなければいい」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]梨深[line]Then never open your eyes again.[%p]"

msgid "16800:野呂瀬の胸に、圧迫感。[linebreak]次いで脳に届く、痛みの信号。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:Norose felt a pressure in his chest, and then a pain signal reached his brain.[%p]"

msgid "16900:霧が晴れるかのように、覆い尽くしていた瞳はすべて消えた。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:The eyes all disappeared, like a lifting fog.[%p]"

msgid "17000:野呂瀬の目の前に、梨深の姿。[linebreak]その手に握った、十字の杭は。[linebreak]野呂瀬の胸に、深々と突き刺さっていて。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:Rimi was right in front of him. And the cross-shaped stake in her hand... was stabbed deep into his chest.[%p]"

msgid "17100:野呂瀬は絶命していた。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:Norose was dead.[%p]"

msgid "17200:梨深は、野呂瀬の死を確かめてから、がっくりとその場に膝を突いた。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:After she was sure he was gone, Rimi dropped helplessly to her knees.[%p]"

msgid "17300:出血がひどく、顔色は陶器のように白い。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:She was bleeding badly, and her face was pale and clammy.[%p]"

msgid "17400:もはやほとんど意識はなく。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:She was barely even conscious.[%p]"

msgid "17500:苦しそうに、小刻みな吐息を漏らしている。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:Her breathing was ragged and painful.[%p]"

msgid "17600:すでに、その目はなにも見ていない。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:Her vision had already gone dark.[%p]"

msgid "17700:いまだ健在であるノアⅡの不気味な稼働音は、かろうじて耳に届いてはいる。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:She could just barely make out the eerie sounds made by the still-functional Noah II.[%p]"

msgid "17800:――でも、あれを壊すのは、他の人に、託すしかなさそうかな。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:But I'm probably going to need someone else to destroy it.[%p]"

msgid "17900:[name]梨深[line]「ごめんね、タク……」[%p]"
msgstr "17900:[name]梨深[line]I'm sorry, Taku.[%p]"

msgid "18000:ぽつりと、梨深はつぶやく。[linebreak]ほとんど声にならないほどの、かすかな声。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:She whispered, her voice barely audible.[%p]"

msgid "18100:[name]梨深[line]「約束、守れそうに、ないみたい……」[%p]"
msgstr "18100:[name]梨深[line]I don't think I can keep my promise.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]梨深[line]「ナナちゃん、助けたから……それで、罪滅ぼしなんかには……ならないけど……助けた……から……」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]梨深[line]I saved Nana. I know that doesn't make up for what I did, but... I saved her.[%p]"

msgid "18300:梨深は、のろのろと顔を上げた。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:She slowly raised her head.[%p]"

msgid "18400:プラネタリウムの壁の一部は、崩れているはずだった。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:She couldn't see it, but the wall of the planetarium in front of her was shattered.[%p]"

msgid "18500:そこから、空がのぞいているはずだった。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:Beyond it lay the sky.[%p]"

msgid "18600:さっきは雨雲に覆われていた。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:It had been raining a moment ago.[%p]"

msgid "18700:今はどうだろう。[linebreak]彼女の目では、その空の色を確かめることはもうできないけれど――[%p]"
msgstr "18700:But what about now? She couldn't see what color the sky was now, but...[%p]"

msgid "18800:咲畑梨深は、空を見上げて、わずかに、微笑んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:She looked up at it and smiled, just a little.[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]梨深[line]「あの空を……あなたと、もう一度見たかったな……」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]梨深[line]I wish I could've seen that sky with you again.[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]梨深[line]「タク……ありがとう……」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]梨深[line]Taku... Thank you.[%p]"

